rTypeName":"word"},{"id":82004,"position":11,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ","translation":"উপর তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_162_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82005,"position":12,"arabic":"رِجْزًۭا","translation":"শাস্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_162_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82006,"position":13,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_162_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82007,"position":14,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءِ","translation":"আকাশ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_162_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82008,"position":15,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"এ কারণে যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_162_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82009,"position":16,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","translation":"তারা ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_162_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82010,"position":17,"arabic":"يَظْلِمُونَ","translation":"তারা সীমালঙ্ঘন করতে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_162_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82011,"position":18,"arabic":"١٦٢","translation":"(১৬২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":163,"arabic":"وَسْـَٔلْهُمْ عَنِ ٱلْقَرْيَةِ ٱلَّتِى كَانَتْ حَاضِرَةَ ٱلْبَحْرِ إِذْ يَعْدُونَ فِى ٱلسَّبْتِ إِذْ تَأْتِيهِمْ حِيتَانُهُمْ يَوْمَ سَبْتِهِمْ شُرَّعًۭا وَيَوْمَ لَا يَسْبِتُونَ ۙ لَا تَأْتِيهِمْ ۚ كَذَٰلِكَ نَبْلُوهُم بِمَا كَانُوا۟ يَفْسُقُونَ","translation":"And ask them about that town which stood by the sea: how its people would profane the Sabbath whenever their fish came to them, breaking the water's surface, on a day on which they ought to have kept Sabbath -because they would not come to them on other than Sabbath-days! Thus did We try them by means of their [own] iniquitous doings.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1117.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":82116,"position":1,"arabic":"وَسْـَٔلْهُمْ","translation":"এবং জিজ্ঞেস করো তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_163_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82117,"position":2,"arabic":"عَنِ","translation":"সম্বন্ধে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_163_002.mp3","charTypeName":"wo